name: Marillina Nadin
description: I’m an outgoing romantic,caring person.My glass is always half full,being an optimist,life is an adventure.I’m willing to try new things,you never know until you try,i.e.this adlol.I am honest and appreciate honesty from others.I don’t have time formind games.Whoever you are and whatever you are is the way it should be.No sense in making yourself into someone you are not, too much drama.It’s better to bestraight up at the beginning and allow the other person to choose if you fit into their world.
